data.description: Step into luxury with this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom 2-story brick home with a 3 car garage in beautiful Stokesdale. Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the seamless blend of modern elegance and classic charm. The spacious living area features newly refinished floors that radiate throughout the main level.Prepare to be impressed by the kitchen, adorned with sleek granite countertops. For those who love the outdoors, the backyard is a true haven. Stretching expansively behind the home, its possibilities are endless. The covered deck invites you to savor your morning coffee or host memorable gatherings with friends and family. Inside, a substantial bonus room that can be used as a flex room, for those who crave storage, the  attic on the upper level provides ample storage and opportunies. Solar panels on the home are a great added feature and you can't miss the large 3 car garage.Schedule your showing today! USDA Eligable, Seller to pay $3000 in closing w acceptable offer.
